    excerpt: "Introduction to activities for 3-month-olds: Explore 29 creative ways to play and learn with your baby during their critical early months. From sensory playtime to heartwarming cuddles, each activity fosters sensory development and strengthens your bond. Adapt activities to your baby's unique pace and preferences, always prioritizing safety and comfort. Cherish these early moments of discovery.",
